    <name>AMCIS Security Platform</name>
    <summary>Autonomous Multidimensional Cyber Intelligence System</summary>
    
    <description>
        <p>
            AMCIS is a next-generation cybersecurity platform designed for government agencies
            and enterprises requiring quantum-resistant security and automated compliance.
        </p>
        <p>Key Features:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Post-quantum cryptography (CRYSTALS-Kyber, CRYSTALS-Dilithium)</li>
            <li>AI-powered threat detection and response</li>
            <li>Federal compliance automation (NIST CSF, FedRAMP, CMMC)</li>
            <li>Zero-trust network architecture</li>
            <li>Security orchestration and automated response (SOAR)</li>
            <li>Supply chain security with SBOM generation</li>
        </ul>
    </description>
    
